"2 tablespoon olive oil","1/4 pound hard salami (such as Genoa), cut into 1/4-inch cubes","1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","1 tablespoon honey","2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","1/8 teaspoon kosher salt","1/8 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/2  red onion, sliced into rings","6 cups (about 9 ounces) spinach, cleaned and stemmed","4  eggs, hard-boiled"